  ZABBIX 4.0 SERVER SETUP  
  Complete Installation Guide: Commands, Configs & Setup  

1. OVERVIEW
This guide covers the complete setup of Zabbix 4.0 on CentOS/RHEL with MariaDB as shown in the installation screenshots. It includes all terminal commands, configuration files, database setup, and web frontend installation.

