11. Zabbix Agent Configuration
Edit the Zabbix agent config file on monitored hosts:

vi /etc/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.conf

Key settings in zabbix_agentd.conf:
# --- /etc/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.conf ---
PidFile=/var/run/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.pid
LogFile=/var/log/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.log
LogFileSize=0

# Zabbix server IP (allow connections from)
Server=192.168.182.139

# Active agent - server IP for active checks
ServerActive=192.168.182.139

# Hostname must match the hostname in Zabbix web frontend
Hostname=Zabbix server

