14. Troubleshooting Commands
Check service logs:
tail -f /var/log/zabbix/zabbix_server.log
tail -f /var/log/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.log
tail -f /var/log/httpd/error_log

Check service status:
systemctl status zabbix-server
systemctl status zabbix-agent
netstat -tlnp | grep 10051
netstat -tlnp | grep 10050

Test DB connection:
mysql -u zabbix -p zabbix -e 'SELECT COUNT(*) FROM hosts;'

Fix agent unreachable (Screenshot 5 alert):
# Check agent config
grep '^Server' /etc/zabbix/zabbix_agentd.conf

# Must match Zabbix server IP
# Server=192.168.182.139

# Restart agent
systemctl restart zabbix-agent

